Spinister had prepared to blast both of them, but Havotron beat him to
it. He slowly turned away, walking towards Needlenose. "Needlenose, take
Slugslinger into space." he whispered. "Get close to the autobots." 

Nightmare looked straight at Havotron, then saluted. "Yessss ssssir."
His hoarse voice whispered.

Jagged was to busy licking his wounds to be bothered. He did give a
dirty look to Quake, and held up his gun, pretending to shoot Quake.
Satisfied he turned, and in a sad tone said, "Yes Havotron, I will try
to do you credit."
